25|$|The Clare Boothe Luce Award, {{established}} in 1991 {{in memory of}} Luce, is The Heritage Foundation's highest award for distinguished contributions to the conservative movement. Prominent recipients include Ronald Reagan, Margaret Thatcher, and William <b>F.</b> <b>Buckley</b> Jr.|$|E
